The defence in the Senzo Meyiwa trial says it can link Kelly Khumalo directly to the murder. Advocate Malesela Teffo says a witness will testify that the singer allegedly pulled the trigger. Courtesy #DStv403 #eNCA  JOHANNESBURG - The defence in the Senzo Meyiwa trial says it can link Kelly Khumalo directly to the murder. Advocate Malesela Teffo says a witness will testify that the singer allegedly pulled the trigger. READ: Docuseries crew to stay in court as Meyiwa murder trial continues He was cross-examining forensic officer Thabo Mosia on Wednesday. Teffo insists the trial is part of a massive cover-up to protect the killer. Watch the video above for more details. 